title: Oat Milk
description: A small 100% vegan/vegetarian cafe, opened in August 2015, serving coffee, tea, sandwiches, snacks and cakes. A range of non dairy milks is available, not just oat milk.  Much of the food is vegan. The cafe is decked out with old music studio equipment, and aims to be a hang out for musicians and artists, with a recording space in the basement. Slogan is Peace. Love. Audio.
